<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customer Reviews - कृषी-सेतू</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
    <style>
        .reviews-page {
            padding: 100px 0 80px;
            background-color: #f5f5dc;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .reviews-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        
        .reviews-header h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #2c5f2d;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
        
        .reviews-header p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .reviews-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .reviews-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        
        .stat-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .stat-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .stat-box i {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #8bc34a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .stat-box h3 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #2c5f2d;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .stat-box p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .all-reviews-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .back-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: #2c5f2d;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .back-link:hover {
            color: #8bc34a;
            transform: translateX(-5px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <section class="reviews-page">
        <div class="reviews-container">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home
            </a>
            
            <div class="reviews-header">
                <h1>What Our Customers Say</h1>
                <p>Real stories from people who love farm-fresh produce</p>
            </div>

            <div class="reviews-stats">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <h3>4.9/5</h3>
                    <p>Average Rating</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    <h3>10,000+</h3>
                    <p>Happy Customers</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                    <h3>5,000+</h3>
                    <p>Reviews</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i>
                    <h3>98%</h3>
                    <p>Satisfaction Rate</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="all-reviews-grid">
                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust1.jpg" alt="Shashank Sanmukh Kanade" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>I was impressed by how smooth the process was and how well they understood our needs. The result exceeded our expectations, and we're very happy.</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Shashank Sanmukh Kanade</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust3.jpg" alt="Atharv Kiran Holsambre" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>From start to finish, their team was responsive, friendly, and genuinely invested in helping us succeed. They go above and beyond, and it shows in the results.</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Atharv Kiran Holsambre</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust4.jpg" alt="Sarang Pradeep Jadhav" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>Professional and reliable service. Easy to work with and highly recommended!</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Sarang Pradeep Jadhav</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust5.jpg" alt="Atharv Rajan Mulik" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>They delivered exactly what we needed. Great quality and on time!</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Atharv Rajan Mulik</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust2.jpg" alt="Soham Appasaheb Thopate" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>Handled everything efficiently and met expectations without issues. Solid service, responsive, and easy to coordinate with. Highly recommended!</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Soham Appasaheb Thopate</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust6.jpg" alt="Priya Sharma" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>The freshness and quality of the vegetables are unmatched. I love supporting local farmers through this platform!</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Priya Sharma</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust7.jpg" alt="Rajesh Patil" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>Best decision I made was joining Krishi Setu. Direct connection with farmers means better prices and fresher produce!</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Rajesh Patil</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="review">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <img src="/images/cust8.jpg" alt="Sneha Deshmukh" class="review-avatar"/>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-content">
                        <p>Amazing platform! The organic vegetables taste so much better than store-bought ones. Will definitely order again!</p>
                        <p class="review-author">Sneha Deshmukh</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/landing.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
